description:
The Jan. 6 hearings are just the 3rd Trump impeachment in desperate attempt to energize their base. Clay, the Nashville Nostradamus, predicts a DeSantis vs. Trump 2024 GOP primary. Jedediah Bila joins Clay and Buck with her mama bear claws out over drag shows for kids. As the country falls apart now, Biden's talking about climate change.
